summary: A cozy getaway from killing, pillaging and being a hero.
descriptionHtml:
Acozy cottage originally built for Lord Arundel near half-moon mill. Although the original structure is gone a group of companions built this abode in hopes that Lord Arundel would return to care for his garden and hunt wild bears.
Has enchanting, alchemy, forging equipment, storage, etc(all the essential stuff)
Add it has four followers.
(My brother requested I make him a house so here it is)
author: NonstronKutless
